- Chapter 2: Pygame Basics
        We covered basic functions and learned what modules are.
        What GUI and CLI means and how they work and they cannot display graphics.
        How to import pygame and its system.
        We learnt about Game loops and game states. They handle events, draws and updates the game state.
        Event objects (pygame.event.Event)
        Coordinates and how we might use them.
        Colors and transparent colours (RGB, DISPLAYSURF, pygame.Color)
        Rect Objects and how to draw shapes.
        Primitive Drawing functions. To draw ellipses, circles or lines.
        pygame.draw functions.
        Pixel Array objects and how to use them.
        Animation and how to update display.

